---
layout: base.njk
title: Workshops & Tutorials
description: "Five accepted workshops at ACM CAIS 2026 covering AI agents, reinforcement learning, agentic software engineering, and more. Join us May 26 in San Jose."
permalink: /pages/workshops/
extraStyles: |
  /* Workshops-specific styles */
  .section-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .2px;
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--eerie-black);
  }

  .anchor {
    scroll-margin-top: 84px;
  }

  .card-quiet {
    border: 1px solid var(--silver);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--seasalt);
    transition: border-color 200ms linear, box-shadow 200ms linear;
  }

  .card-quiet:hover {
    border-color: var(--olive-moss);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .workshop-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .workshop-link:hover {
    color: inherit;
  }

  .workshop-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--terracotta-deep);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight-box {
    background: rgba(149, 108, 88, 0.05);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--platinum);
  }

  .dates-card {
    border: 2px solid var(--terracotta-deep);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
  }
---
{% from "subscribe-form.njk" import subscribe %}

<header class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold">Workshops &amp; Tutorials</h1>
        <p class="lead mb-3">{{ site.fullName }} ({{ site.name }})</p>
        <p class="mb-0"><strong>{{ site.location }} &bull; {{ site.dates.workshops }}</strong></p>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <!-- Main Content Column -->
            <div class="col-lg-8">

                <!-- Accepted Workshops -->
                <section id="workshops" class="anchor mb-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Accepted Workshops</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">Five workshops have been accepted for the inaugural CAIS workshop day on <strong>Tuesday, May 26, 2026</strong>. Workshop attendance is included with conference registration. Visit each workshop's website for submission details and schedules.</p>

                    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">

                        <a href="https://ai-discovery-in-the-wild.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="workshop-link">
                            <div class="card-quiet d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="workshop-number mt-1">1</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">AI Agents for Discovery in the Wild</h3>
                                    <span class="small text-muted"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right me-1"></i>ai-discovery-in-the-wild.github.io</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://rl-eval.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="workshop-link">
                            <div class="card-quiet d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="workshop-number mt-1">2</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">RLEval: Methods and Reinforcement Learning Environments for Evaluating AI Agents</h3>
                                    <span class="small text-muted"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right me-1"></i>rl-eval.github.io</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://bauplanlabs.github.io/SAO-workshop/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="workshop-link">
                            <div class="card-quiet d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="workshop-number mt-1">3</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Supporting Our AI Overlords (SAO)</h3>
                                    <span class="small text-muted"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right me-1"></i>bauplanlabs.github.io/SAO-workshop</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://agentskills-workshop.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="workshop-link">
                            <div class="card-quiet d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="workshop-number mt-1">4</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Agent Skills 2026</h3>
                                    <span class="small text-muted"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right me-1"></i>agentskills-workshop.github.io</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                        <a href="https://agenticse-cais.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="workshop-link">
                            <div class="card-quiet d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                                <span class="workshop-number mt-1">5</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">Agentic Software Engineering</h3>
                                    <span class="small text-muted"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right me-1"></i>agenticse-cais.github.io</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>

                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Workshop Timeline -->
                <section id="timeline" class="anchor mb-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Important Dates</h2>

                    <div class="alert alert-warning mb-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i><strong>Note:</strong> Individual workshop deadlines may vary. Please check each workshop's website for specific submission and notification dates.
                    </div>

                    <table class="table table-sm mb-4">
                        <tbody>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Suggested Submission Date for Workshop Contributions</td>
                                <td class="text-end"><strong>Sun, April 12, 2026</strong></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>Mandatory Accept/Reject Notification Date</td>
                                <td class="text-end"><strong>Tue, May 5, 2026</strong> (tentative)</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="table-active">
                                <td><strong>Workshops &amp; Tutorials Day</strong></td>
                                <td class="text-end"><strong>Tue, May 26, 2026</strong></td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </section>

                <!-- Organizer Support -->
                <section id="support" class="anchor mb-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Attendee Information</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>There is <strong>no separate workshop registration</strong>. Workshop attendance is included with conference registration.</li>
                        <li>All workshops take place <strong>in-person at the conference venue</strong> on Tuesday, May 26.</li>
                        <li><strong>Coffee breaks and lunch</strong> are provided.</li>
                        <li>A <strong>common poster and demonstration session</strong> will be held during the extended afternoon coffee break.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>For workshop organizers:</strong> Workshop organizers are responsible for creating their own website and publishing versions of workshop papers. CAIS does not provide support for official workshop proceedings.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Workshop Chairs -->
                <section id="chairs" class="anchor mb-5">
                    <h2 class="section-title h4 mb-3">Workshop Co-Chairs</h2>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="/assets/images/Raghavan_Deepti.png" alt="Deepti Raghavan" class="rounded-circle me-3" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-0"><a href="https://deeptir.me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deepti Raghavan</a></h3>
                                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Brown University</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                <img src="/assets/images/chen_lingjiao.png" alt="Lingjiao Chen" class="rounded-circle me-3" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <div>
                                    <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-0"><a href="https://lchen001.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lingjiao Chen</a></h3>
                                    <p class="small text-muted mb-0">Microsoft Research</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

            </div>

            <!-- Sidebar -->
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <aside>
                    <!-- Key Dates -->
                    <div class="card dates-card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2"></i>Key Dates</h3>

                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <div class="border-start ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left-width: 3px !important; border-color: var(--davys-gray) !important;">
                                    <div class="fw-bold small">Workshop Contributions Due</div>
                                    <div class="small">Sun, April 12, 2026</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="border-start ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left-width: 3px !important; border-color: var(--davys-gray) !important;">
                                    <div class="fw-bold small">Accept/Reject Notification</div>
                                    <div class="small">Tue, May 5, 2026 (tentative)</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="border-start ps-3" style="border-left-width: 3px !important; border-color: var(--terracotta-deep) !important;">
                                    <div class="fw-bold small">Workshops &amp; Tutorials Day</div>
                                    <div class="small">Tue, May 26, 2026</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <p class="text-muted small mb-0"><i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>Check individual workshop sites for exact deadlines</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Workshop Quick Links -->
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-collection me-2"></i>Workshops</h3>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 small">
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="https://ai-discovery-in-the-wild.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AI Agents for Discovery in the Wild <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right" style="font-size: 0.7rem;"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="https://rl-eval.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RLEval <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right" style="font-size: 0.7rem;"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="https://bauplanlabs.github.io/SAO-workshop/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Supporting Our AI Overlords (SAO) <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right" style="font-size: 0.7rem;"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="https://agentskills-workshop.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Agent Skills 2026 <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right" style="font-size: 0.7rem;"></i></a></li>
                                <li class="mb-0"><a href="https://agenticse-cais.github.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Agentic Software Engineering <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-up-right" style="font-size: 0.7rem;"></i></a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Stay Updated -->
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3">Stay Updated</h3>
                            <p class="small mb-3">Get conference and program updates.</p>
                            {{ subscribe(layout="stacked", inputId="bd-email-workshops") }}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Page Links -->
                    <div class="card mb-4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-link-45deg me-2"></i>On This Page</h3>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#workshops">Accepted Workshops</a></li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#timeline">Important Dates</a></li>
                                <li class="mb-2"><a href="#support">Attendee Information</a></li>
                                <li class="mb-0"><a href="#chairs">Workshop Co-Chairs</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Questions -->
                    <div class="highlight-box mb-3">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">Workshop Questions?</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-2">Questions about workshops, submissions, or scheduling.</p>
                        <p class="small mb-0"><a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.workshopChairs }}">{{ site.contact.workshopChairs }}</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h3 class="h6 fw-bold mb-2">General Inquiries</h3>
                        <p class="small text-muted mb-2">Registration, logistics, and other conference questions.</p>
                        <p class="small mb-0"><a href="mailto:{{ site.contact.email }}">{{ site.contact.email }}</a></p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
